{
  "stem": "13313.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As soon as he did that, I turned around and I just disappeared.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I vanished.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no way I was going to talk to an SS, no matter what.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my brother showed up about an hour later.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He, with another kid, had run to the front of the building.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the other kid wanted to cross the street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My brother didn't want to cross the street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Instinct-- stayed there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as he crossed the street, my brother-- little kid-- a bomb hit and killed that little kid in front of my brother's eyes.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Across the street was a French Catholic private school, Institute [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "All the kids were in the basement sheltered and they all suffocated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They all died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Just across the street.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The next time I saw my brother he was on the knees of the dentist or doctor, from me to him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was a little child.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He, he was [INAUDIBLE] to see that little boy that got killed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "What had happened was that the tactic of the American Air Force was that when it went after the target, they would send out a reconnaissance plane that would then draw a circle of smoke over the target.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then those who dropped their bombs in there was supposed to follow the target.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But, but between being chased by Messerschmitts and, and not being able to communicate with other troops, he drew in a circle, instead of over the factory, right over the heart of the town, of the town.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were exactly in the focal point of this bombardment. 1,500 people died just within a few hundred yards of where we were.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Every year on April the 5th, there's a big commemoration with a, with a, with a big parade to commemorate that.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
